                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8110" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OB-0372</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2709 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">推倒心墙：春城湖畔员工满意度到敬业度的激活之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Toppling the Heart Wall: The Journey from Employee Satisfaction to Engagement at the Spring City</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">黄波，王延玲（通讯作者），陈兰兰，谭茹方，唐嵩，田迪，陈维清，张秋艳</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">昆明春城湖畔旅游置业发展有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">6 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">敬业度；满意度；影响因素；激励；微案例none</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">employee engagement, satisfaction, influencing factors, incentives</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">春城湖畔度假村（简称春城湖畔）为了应对经济下行压力，决定全面建设员工敬业度项目以提高服务品质，推动企业战略发展，力将春城湖畔创建成为“全球最受钦佩的高尔夫度假村”。本案例根据实际情况分析了春城湖畔推行员工敬业度项目的背景及原因，并从战略部署、战术激励、全面改进、未来展望四个方面详细阐述了春城湖畔员工敬业度项目的建设内容和发展过程。案例通过对春城湖畔员工敬业度项目的成长过程描述，配合案例提出的问题，帮助读者辩证性地理解、分析和掌握员工敬业度的含义、内容、影响因素及敬业度项目的运行框架和作用机制。同时，案例为更多企业在践行员工敬业度项目或其他员工管理活动时，提供了全面且具有可操作性的方向和策略，具有较高的参考和借鉴价值。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In response to the economic downturn pressure, the Spring City Golf &amp;Lake Resort has decided to comprehensively implement an employee engagement project to improve its service quality and strive to establish itself as the &quot;world&#39;s most admired golf resort.&quot; This case analyzes the background and reasons for the implementation of the employee engagement project at the Spring City, and provides detailed descriptions of the project&#39;s construction and development process from the strategic deployment, tactical incentives, comprehensive improvement, and future prospects. By describing the establishment process of the employee engagement project at the Spring City and addressing the questions raised in the case study, it helps readers dialectically understand, analyze, and grasp the meaning, content, influencing factors, operational framework, and the mechanism of the employee engagement. Furthermore, the case  is of significant practical implications by guiding the directions and offering replicable action plans for more companies to practice employee engagement projects or other employee management activities.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《组织行为学》、《领导学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">员工满意度和员工敬业度的区别与联系；敬业度与企业绩效的关系；工作需求-资源模型（JD-R）；双因素理论；员工敬业度的驱动因素等相关知识点。</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-01</td>
                            </tr>
